vision_lesson_boundary('IM-G6-U2-L15', "Every extracted task is whole-number or decimal addition, multiplication, or division, and each maps to an existing automaton: repeat_equal_groups for the \"N parts x value-per-part\" products, fair_share_equal_groups for the partitive \"total shared into a known number of parts\" quotients, measure_groups_of_size for the one quotitive quotient (divide(80,8): how many 8-ml batches are in 80 ml), and base_ones_chunking as the neutral default for the additions, since the worked solutions state sums as results without showing a method. No task demands an operation lacking an automaton. The lesson's a").

