vision_lesson_boundary('IM-G6-U4-L11', "Every demanded operation has a fraction-category automaton; none falls outside the vocabulary. The warm-up demands fraction multiplication (area_model_part_of_part for the fraction-by-fraction products; unit_fraction_iteration for 1/8*8, which reconstructs a whole from eight unit fractions). Every quotient task is fraction division introduced as measurement division (\"how many b's are in a\"), carried by measurement_division. The lesson's own arc develops the reciprocal/product-rule algorithm (divide by a/b = multiply by b, divide by a), which the vocabulary carries SEPARATELY as unit_fraction_").

