vision_lesson_goal('IM-G6-U6-L5', teacher, "Interpret and coordinate sentences and equations that represent a situation.").
vision_lesson_goal('IM-G6-U6-L5', teacher, "State explicitly (orally and in writing) what the chosen variable represents in an equation.").
vision_lesson_goal('IM-G6-U6-L5', teacher, "Use equations in the form x + p = q or px = q to solve real-world problems and explain (orally) the solution method.").
vision_lesson_goal('IM-G6-U6-L5', student, "Let's use equations to represent and solve real-world problems.").
vision_lesson_purpose('IM-G6-U6-L5', "In this lesson, students apply what they have learned about variables and equations to represent and solve real-world problems. Students must decontextualize the situation and represent it symbolically, and then interpret the results of any calculation in context.").
