vision_lesson_purpose('IM-G6-U9-L10', "This lesson is optional. In this exploration in pure mathematics, students tackle a series of activities that explore the relationship between the greatest common factor of two numbers and related fractions using a geometric representation. The activities in this lesson build on each other, providing students an opportunity to express the relationship between the greatest common factor of two numbers and related fractions through repeated reasoning (MP8).").
