vision_lesson_boundary('IM-G7-U1-L11', "Scales without units express pure multiplicative relationships independent of the measuring unit chosen. Students often mistake these for permission to use different units for scaled versus actual measurements, or treat them as unit-conversion problems rather than recognizing the unit-independent scale factor.").

