vision_lesson_boundary('IM-G7-U1-L13', "This culminating project requires students to coordinate measurement, scale selection, and drawing to map their actual classroom—synthesizing all prior scaling work into a real-world application. Students typically struggle most with choosing a scale strategically, balancing the constraint of fitting the drawing on paper against keeping details legible, and with maintaining measurement accuracy across a group.").

