vision_lesson_purpose('IM-G7-U3-L6', "Students practice decomposing irregular regions into familiar shapes (rectangles and triangles) to calculate exact areas from floor plans and estimate areas from map regions. This prepares them for estimating areas of circles in the next lesson.").
