vision_lesson_purpose('IM-G7-U3-L9', "In this lesson, students apply the formula A = πr² to solve problems involving the area of shapes made up of parts of circles and other shapes such as rectangles (MP7). Students are also introduced to the idea of expressing exact answers in terms of π (MP6).").
