vision_lesson_boundary('IM-G7-U4-L1', "Beyond applying a known ratio (scale_ratio_unit), the lesson demands two moves the automaton vocabulary has no dedicated strategy for, so they are marked NONE. (1) Deriving a scale factor from two corresponding lengths (warm-up divisions 4/2, 6/3 and practice problem 2's 11/2): scale_ratio_unit applies a ratio but no automaton computes one from measured sides. (2) Finding what percent one quantity is of another (Laos red 300/600, union 41/190, union-red 78.875/190): there is no percentage automaton. The France flag's three equal bands (100/3) are the exception — an equal partition that maps cl").

