vision_lesson_boundary('IM-G7-U6-L7', "This checkpoint assesses students' ability to coordinate symbolic equations with visual (hanger diagram) and contextual (purchase scenario) representations. Students often struggle to connect equation structure—particularly how distributive relationships like 5(x + 4) combine operations—with diagram parts or real-world quantities. A common error is confusing variable meanings, such as treating the cost per unit the same as the number of units ordered.").

