vision_lesson_purpose('IM-G7-U7-L1', "In this lesson, students gain hands-on experience composing, decomposing, and measuring angles. Students connect vocabulary such as right angles and straight angles with their degree measures, as well as the description of going all the way around a point as 360 degrees. Students fit pattern blocks around a point using these relationships to determine the unknown angles on the remaining pattern blocks. Students use the structure of the blocks completely going around a point with no gaps to solve for angles (MP7).").
