vision_lesson_boundary('IM-G8-U4-L2', "This lesson bridges concrete hanger balance to algebraic equation solving by establishing that equal operations on both sides maintain equivalence. Students often mistake equation moves (subtracting from both sides) for arbitrary rules rather than genuine preservation of equality grounded in the physical balance principle.").

vision_lesson('IM-G8-U4-L3', 8, 4, 3, "Balanced Moves").
